System Requirements:

* Kali Linux OS (you can install Virutal Box on Kali Linux)
* Android Device or Emulator
* Internet Access

Software tool Requirements:

* Keytool (preinstalled in kali linux)
* jar signer (preinstalled in kali linux)
* zipalign (need to install)

NOTE: If keytool command not found. Try to update using  command 
root@kali:~# sudo apt update

Install Java in Kali
root@kali:~# sudo apt install -y default-jdk
//check using following command whether java installed successfully.
root@kali:~# java -version

Install Zipalign
root@kali:~# apt-get install zipalign
